            "\u201cBe broken, you peoples, and be shattered;\nAnd listen, all remote places of the earth.\nGet ready, yet be shattered;\nGet ready, yet be shattered.",
            "\u201cDevise a plan, but it will fail;\nState a proposal, but it will not stand,\nFor God is with us.\u201d",
